{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_13_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 養成所の先生",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん。次のライブで着る新衣装のことで話が……\nうん？　どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.011292553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、{user}君。お疲れ様\nそれが、ちょっと困ったことになっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9779592197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "今日の番組で共演する新人アイドルの子が\nテレビの仕事が初めてらしくて緊張していたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1446258863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.6446258863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "だから緊張をほぐしてあげようと思って\n私から声を掛けたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1779592197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.8446258863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（BIG4のサニピはライバル視されることも多い）\n（もしかして、敵視されて酷いことを言われたのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.4964172682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "……その子に物凄く懐かれて、目をウルウルさせながら\n「お姉様と呼ばせて下さい」ってお願いされたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3630839349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "仲良くなれたのは嬉しいけど\nどう反応したらいいのか困っちゃったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9630839349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.5297506016
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは昔から共演者やスタッフに\n好かれますよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.7918828172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "好かれてるかは分からないけど\n話しやすいって言ってもらえることはよくあるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3918828172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それで「君の資質はアイドルよりも裏方向きだ」って\n制作会社からスカウトされたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3585494838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.0918828172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "「君には年齢以上の落ち着きと貫禄がある」\nなんて感心されて、複雑な心境になることもあったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6585494838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0918828172
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "話しやすいからなのか、たまに共演者の方や\nスタッフさんから悩みを相談されることもあるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0918828172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "どうして年上の人が、ピチピチの十七歳の私に\n人生相談をするのかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5252161505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "十七歳じゃないですけどね……\n遙子さんはそれだけ信頼して話せる相手ってことですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんには、なんと言うか……\n包容力や母性を感じるような安心感がありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.9238106254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "母性って褒め方をたまにされるけど\nピチピチの十七歳としては素直に喜べないわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2904772921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは、人から頼られるのが嫌なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.8571439587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.516237148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわよ。頼ってもらえるのは嬉しいし\n頼られたら私も力になりたいと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.116237148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "私も昔、辛かった時期に\n尊敬する先輩に相談して救われたことがあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.716237148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.116237148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "以前話してくれた星村さんのことですね\n元トップアイドルで今はプロデューサーをしている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ\n私がアイドルを目指すきっかけになった、憧れの人よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4811577961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.9811577961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "星村さんは悩んでいた私の背中を押してくれた……\n私もそんな先輩でありたいと思ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3811577961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.0811628823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "今は後進の育成に力を注いでいて\n表舞台にはあまり出て来ないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.8144962156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "いつか、星村さんともお仕事をしてみたいわね\n次に会えるのはいつになるかしら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1144962156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.7811628823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 184.8811628823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが、私に頼み事を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.881153727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんでも、昔からの知り合いで、借りがある相手から\n頼まれて、断れなかったそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.4000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが断れないなんて、よっぽどの相手なのね\n一体どんな借りを作ったのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.619190455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それが、I-UNITYの時に\n裏で助けてもらっていたらしくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITY……。なら、知らないところで\n私達もその人に助けられていたかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.5666506932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "それで、私に頼みたいことって何かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.4666415379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "芸能プロダクションが運営するアイドル養成所で\nデビュー前の新人を指導してほしいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.1333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "私が養成所の先生になって教えるの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.1933764623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "指導と言っても、一日だけの特別講師ですから\nそれほど深刻に考えなくていいと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.1000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私はアイドルとして全然人気が出なかったのよ\nそんな私がアイドルについて偉そうに語るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.4551773237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "私じゃ新人のお手本にはならないわ\n講師にはもっとふさわしい人がいるんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.5551773237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんですか。今の遙子さんは誰もが認める\nトップアイドルです。自信を持って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.7333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、以前サニピが全国ツアーをした時にも\nタレントスクールの講師をしたじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.3333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "あれはサプライズで、ファンレターをくれた子達に\n楽しんでもらうのが目的だったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 273.2324593393,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "芸能プロが運営する養成所で、デビュー前の新人を\n指導するのとでは責任の重みが違うわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 280.700008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、活躍してるアイドルなら他にも大勢いるのに\nどうしてわざわざ売れないアイドルだった私に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "理由は分かりませんが\n先方が直々に遙子さんを指名したそうですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 296.1666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko Saeki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "先方？　そういえば、芸能プロの養成所って\n言ってたけど、どこのプロダクションなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.2399197428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_13_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんに講師を依頼してきたのは……\nバンプロダクションの養成所です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.7666748047,
      "sfxList": []
